# Software Requirements Specification (SRS)

# Smart Assignment Management System

## 1. Introduction

### 1.1 Project Title

Smart Assignment Management System

### 1.2 Purpose

The purpose of this system is to digitize and automate assignment creation, submission, approval, rejection, communication, and reporting activities between students and faculty while providing administrators with complete control and analytics.

### 1.3 Scope

The platform will allow educational institutions to manage assignments efficiently while supporting individual and team submissions, late submissions, approvals, rejection workflows, notifications, and real-time communication.

---

# 2. Objectives

* Simplify assignment management.
* Reduce manual tracking efforts.
* Enable transparent approval workflows.
* Support team assignments.
* Provide faculty and administrators with analytics.
* Maintain centralized data storage.
* Improve communication between students and faculty.

